ore time accomplishing goals and less time processing  some of vasts finance and real estate investments mighty ripple streeteasy and tala food vasts vision food is human energy and cultural celebration  yesterdays processed foods fed the masses but todays innovation enables everyones access to fresh sustainable nutritious local affordable ingredients  our taste buds and minds should crave fresh produce not high fructose  we look for entrepreneurs throughout the food chain bringing these innovations to the masses  some of vasts investments are sweetgreen juicero gobble and soma happiness vasts vision we love that everyone pursues their own happiness  we look for entrepreneurs who are improving goods or services that already make a lot of people happy  some of vasts happiness investments are bark  co eight fotolog and kiip healthcare vasts vision humans have been around about  million years  weve learned a lot about survival but we still know little about our health  what is good health is it the same for all  we look for entrepreneurs challenging evolutionary thinking  regeneration and restoration vs cures and relief customization and accessibility tracking and measuring in the background while delivering actionable reporting  some of vasts healthcare investments classpass kindara phosphorus recombine and zocdoc resources vasts vision our global population is growing increasingly demanding and surpassing global resources  we seek entrepreneurs that create sustainable and environmentally friendly resources  all kinds foods fragrances pharmaceuticals gems chemicals materials etc  we also look for entrepreneurs harvesting resources beyond earth some of vasts investments are ginkgo bioworks diamond foundry lygos and planetary resources transport  energy vasts vision americans love affair with cars ended in the 9s  no one wants to commute sit in traffic or wait for airport security  we want people to focus on why they travel or transport goods not how  we seek transport entrepreneurs where safety speed and sustainability are assumed not featured  same for energy entrepreneurs  focus on what users do with power not how its received  some of vasts investments firstfuel hyperloop one keychain logistics and mpowerd inspiration collaboration  communityvast ventures believes that ideas with global impact and that aim to do good make great investments  those ideas also create a platform for better ideas and accelerated improvement  we look for opportunities to bring people together and to support events that inspire new ideas collaboration and extended communities  some of our events includevast ventures necker bowl  with the generous hospitality of our friend richard branson vast ventures assembled a group of entrepreneurs and forward thinking corporate partners to discuss global trends and opportunities for improvementft philanthropy and global impact summit vast ventures is proud to sponsor fts inaugural event in bringing together family offices around the globe who are focused on impact investing  copyright  vast ventures management llc david whelan  healthcare growth services firm core services invested search investments venture studio business development design  development organizational development core services invested search investments venture studio business development design  development organizational development about team news careers contact  back david whelan president oxeon ventures david runs oxeon ventures the venture startup studio and investment business at oxeon holdings  the ventures studio designs provides initial capital incubates and builds de novo or purposebuiltfromscratch healthcare companies our team develops and hones concepts and business plans and then leverages oxeon holding’s service lines and vast network of relationships to bring founding leadership productmarket validation enterprise clients and then secure additional capital for these early stage companies we build these companies independently or in partnership with entrepreneursinresidence or codeveloped with outside healthcare companies including leading health systems health plans or technology or service companies companies developed inside of oxeon ventures include docent health risalto and empiric health oxeon ventures also invests in venture and growth stage healthcare technology and service companies including evolent health nyse evh privia acq by brighton holdings liazon acq by towers watson aspire avalon bright capsule ciox imagine health iora health landmark oak street health pager privia quartet vida villagemd wisercare and others david whelan was previously a general partner of accretive llc a private investment firm with a distinctive track record of creating funding and building disruptive technology enabled companies david served as a director on the accretive portfolio company boards of arise virtual solutions and insureon previously david was the chief executive officer of the cloverleaf group a private investment group and prior to that vice president of corporate development with the virgin group in the us and uk where he led the development and startup of virgin america the us based low cost airline david was also an investment banker in london england and sydney australia with goldman sachs  company and before that deutsche bank starting his career at price waterhouse in the firm’s corporate finance division in sydney australia david qualified as a chartered accountant of australia david has a bachelor of laws honours and bachelor of commerce from bond university in queensland australia david also serves on the board of friends of hudson river park trust an independent nonprofit 5c organization dedicated to the completion care and enhancement of the hudsonriver park and is the designated fundraising partner of the hudson river park trust fofhrp creates opportunities for public contributions to and participation in the park’s operations and growth to guarantee its future for generations of new yorkers americans and visitors from around the world david lives in tribeca and with his wife melanie and his two children lachlan and charlotte connect  main office  hudson street suite  new york ny   5 washington dc  silicon valley  oxeon holdings  high risk solutions about us  treadstone healthcare llctreadstone healthcare llc about us homeabout us   about us treadstone healthcare llc is a consulting firm comprised of a syndicate of talent our team members are accomplished in their own disciplines and together we provide a thorough and data driven project experience for our clients our advisory capabilities not only draw on our collective experiences but also leverage our vast network of key opinion leaders in the device biopharma and digital health industries past leadership experiences with companies includes american hospital supply baxter international spacelabs healthcare atl ultrasound ekos corporation intellectual ventures aerojet rocketdyne clearmedical inventiv health general dynamics blue origin and astronics aes we are active members of the medical device and biopharma communities including life sciences washington wings medical device users group pharmaceutical  bioscience society international scip strategic and competitive intelligence professionals and the aca   home  venturehealth email protected8 5 login submit a deal welcome to venturehealthrequest an invite nowventurehealth is currently invite only email i am primarily an  entrepreneur acceredited investor submit already a member  log in forgot your password